@startuml Use Case - GESTION HOBBIES ULTRA-DÉTAILLÉE (User + Code Réel)

!theme plain
skinparam backgroundColor #fefefe
skinparam actorStyle awesome
skinparam packageStyle rectangle

title **Hobbies/Passions - 12+ Cas d'Utilisation Détailés**
actor "👤 User Auth" as User

package "🎯 HobbyController" {
  usecase "📋 Lister hobbies (user()->hobbies()->latest())" as UC_INDEX
  usecase "➕ Créer hobby : name(req), level(?), frequency(?)" as UC_STORE
  usecase "🔄 Toggle status : active ↔ paused (findOrFail $id)" as UC_TOGGLE
  usecase "🗑️ Supprimer hobby (findOrFail $id → delete)" as UC_DESTROY
}

package "🏗️ Modèle Hobby (fillable: user_id, name, level, frequency, status, emoji, progress, description)" {
  usecase "👤 belongsTo User (user_id FK)" as UC_REL1
  usecase "📊 Progress (cast integer 0-100)" as UC_PROGRESS
  usecase "🔍 Scope forUser($userId)" as UC_SCOPE
  usecase "📈 Mettre à jour niveau (1-10 : Débutant→Expert)" as UC_UPDATE_LEVEL
  usecase "⏱️ Fréquence : Quotidien/Semaine/Mois" as UC_FREQ
  usecase "😀 Ajouter emoji personnalisé" as UC_EMOJI
  usecase "📝 Description détaillée" as UC_DESC
  usecase "🎨 hasMany sous-hobbies (hiérarchique)" as UC_SUB
}

package "📱 Vue hobbies.index.blade.php" {
  usecase "🎨 Cards responsive : nom + niveau + status + progress bar" as UC_VIEW
  usecase "➕ Formulaire ajout (validation max:255)" as UC_FORM
  usecase "🔘 Toggle buttons (active/paused)" as UC_BTN_TOGGLE
  usecase "📊 Stats : nombre active/paused, avg niveau" as UC_STATS
}

' LIENS User → Actions
User --> UC_INDEX
User --> UC_STORE
User --> UC_TOGGLE
User --> UC_DESTROY
User --> UC_UPDATE_LEVEL
User --> UC_VIEW

' Détails techniques
UC_STORE ..> "Validation : name req, level/freq nullable" : req->validate()
UC_TOGGLE ..> "Status flip : active→paused↔" 
UC_REL1 ..> User : FK user_id

note right of User
  **Routes** :
  - GET /hobbies → index()
  - POST /hobbies → store()
  - PATCH /hobbies/{id}/toggle
  - DELETE /hobbies/{id}
end note

note bottom of UC_PROGRESS
  **Casts** : progress → integer
  **Champs** : emoji, description
end note

note top
  **Basé sur code réel** HobbyController + Model
  **Messages** : 'success' avec nom hobby
end note

@enduml

